data.description: Welcome to 351 Newman Rd. This beautiful property sits on 4.04 acres with lots of wildlife to oversee. It feels secluded and private. It has 227 ft. from the road to the home. The home features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. It has a loft (that can be framed into a 4th bedroom).  A kitchen with lots of cabinet space. Laundry room is on the main floor. It's a beautiful property on a gorgeous setting. This home will not last long. Contact me today for a private showing.
